show.description: A grieving mother who lost her daughter crosses paths with a single father ready to marry for his child’s sake. As their lives intertwine, a new chapter begins—one shaped by healing, understanding, and unexpected love. Love Refresh is a heartwarming tale of second chances, emotional rebirth, and love born out of shared loss.
